Question: Can you show me the players who scored more than 2 goals in one game? I’d like to see their player_id, name, match number, and how many goals they scored.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no, COUNT(*) AS num_goals
FROM goal_details gd
JOIN player_mast pm ON gd.player_id = pm.player_id
GROUP BY gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no
HAVING COUNT(*) > 2;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no, COUNT(*) AS total_goals
  FROM goal_details gd
  JOIN player_mast pm ON gd.player_id = pm.player_id
  GROUP BY gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 2;

GROUP BY gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no
HAVING COUNT(*) > 2;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no, COUNT(*) AS total_goals
  FROM goal_details gd
  JOIN player_mast pm ON gd.player_id = pm.player_id
  GROUP BY gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 2;

Question: I want to know which matches ended with the same goal count for both teams. Please show match number and the goal score.
Generated SQL Query: SELECT match_no, goal_score FROM match_mast WHERE substring(goal_score FROM '^(\d)') = substring(goal_score FROM '(\d)$');

Question: Saya mau tahu pertandingan mana yang jumlah golnya sama antara dua tim. Tampilkan match_no dan skor golnya ya.
Generated SQL Query: SELECT match_no, goal_score FROM match_mast WHERE goal_score LIKE '__:%__';

Question: Which teams managed to win all their group stage matches? I need to see team_id and how many matches they won.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT team_id, COUNT(*) AS total_wins
FROM match_details
WHERE play_stage = 'G' AND win_lose = 'W'
GROUP BY team_id
HAVING COUNT(*) = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM match_details md2 WHERE md2.team_id = match_details.team_id AND play_stage = 'G');
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT team_id, COUNT(*) AS total_wins
  FROM match_details
  WHERE play_stage = 'G' AND win_lose = 'W'
  GROUP BY team_id
  HAVING COUNT(*) = (
  SELECT COUNT(*) FROM match_details md2
  WHERE md2.team_id = match_details.team_id AND play_stage = 'G'
  );

Question: Can you list referees who led more than 3 matches? I want their referee_id, name, and total matches they officiated.

FROM match_mast mm
JOIN referee_mast rm ON mm.referee_id = rm.referee_id
GROUP BY rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name
HAVING COUNT(*) > 3;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name, COUNT(*) AS total_matches
  FROM match_mast mm
  JOIN referee_mast rm ON mm.referee_id = rm.referee_id
  GROUP BY rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 3;

Question: Show me which players were both substituted in and out in the same game. Include player_id, name, and match number.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT pio.player_id, pm.player_name, pio.match_no
FROM player_in_out pio
JOIN player_mast pm ON pio.player_id = pm.player_id
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM player_in_out p2
    WHERE p2.player_id = pio.player_id
    AND p2.match_no = pio.match_no
    AND p2.in_out != pio.in_out
);
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT pio.player_id, pm.player_name, pio.match_no
  FROM player_in_out pio
  JOIN player_mast pm ON pio.player_id = pm.player_id
  WHERE EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM player_in_out p2
  WHERE p2.player_id = pio.player_id AND p2.match_no = pio.match_no
  AND p2.in_out != pio.in_out
  );

Question: Show me the venues where audience attendance reached the highest. I want venue_name, the city, and the max audience number.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT sv.venue_name, sc.city, MAX(mm.audience) AS max_audience
FROM match_mast mm
JOIN soccer_venue sv ON mm.venue_id = sv.venue_id
JOIN soccer_city sc ON sv.city_id = sc.city_id
GROUP BY sv.venue_name, sc.city
ORDER BY max_audience DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT sv.venue_name, sc.city, MAX(mm.audence) AS max_audience
  FROM match_mast mm
  JOIN soccer_venue sv ON mm.venue_id = sv.venue_id
  JOIN soccer_city sc ON sv.city_id = sc.city_id
  GROUP BY sv.venue_name, sc.city;

Question: Venue mana yang penontonnya paling banyak? Saya mau lihat nama venue, kota, dan jumlah penonton terbanyaknya.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT sv.venue_name, sc.city, MAX(mm.audience) AS max_audience
FROM match_mast mm
JOIN soccer_venue sv ON mm.venue_id = sv.venue_id
JOIN soccer_city sc ON sv.city_id = sc.city_id
GROUP BY sv.venue_name, sc.city
ORDER BY max_audience DESC
LIMIT 1;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT sv.venue_name, sc.city, MAX(mm.audence) AS max_audience
  FROM match_mast mm
  JOIN soccer_venue sv ON mm.venue_id = sv.venue_id
  JOIN soccer_city sc ON sv.city_id = sc.city_id
  GROUP BY sv.venue_name, sc.city;

Question: Find the players who were never substituted out in any match. Please show player_id and their name.
Generated SQL Query:

FROM player_mast pm
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
SELECT 1
FROM player_in_out pio
WHERE pio.player_id = pm.player_id AND pio.in_out = 'O'
);

Question: Can you show players who scored in both the first and second halves of a game? I want player_id, name, and match number.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no
FROM goal_details gd
JOIN player_mast pm ON gd.player_id = pm.player_id
WHERE gd.goal_half = 1
AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM goal_details gd2
    WHERE gd2.player_id = gd.player_id
    AND gd2.match_no = gd.match_no
    AND gd2.goal_half = 2
);
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no
  FROM goal_details gd
  JOIN player_mast pm ON gd.player_id = pm.player_id
  WHERE goal_half = 1
  AND EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM goal_details gd2
  WHERE gd2.player_id = gd.player_id AND gd2.match_no = gd.match_no AND gd2.goal_half = 2
  );

Question: Tampilkan pemain yang cetak gol di babak pertama dan kedua di satu pertandingan. Saya mau lihat player_id, nama, dan match_no-nya.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no
FROM goal_details gd
JOIN player_mast pm ON gd.player_id = pm.player_id
WHERE gd.match_no IN (SELECT match_no FROM goal_details WHERE goal_half = 1)
  AND gd.match_no IN (SELECT match_no FROM goal_details WHERE goal_half = 2)
  AND gd.goal_half IN (1,2)
GROUP BY gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT gd.goal_half) = 2;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT gd.player_id, pm.player_name, gd.match_no
  FROM goal_details gd
  JOIN player_mast pm ON gd.player_id = pm.player_id
  WHERE goal_half = 1
  AND EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM goal_details gd2
  WHERE gd2.player_id = gd.player_id AND gd2.match_no = gd.match_no AND gd2.goal_half = 2
  );

Question: Which players were both involved in goals and received bookings? Show their player_id, name, and how many goals and bookings.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT pm.player_id, pm.player_name,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM goal_details gd WHERE gd.player_id = pm.player_id) AS goal_count,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM player_booked pb WHERE pb.player_id = pm.player_id) AS booking_count
FROM player_mast pm
WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM goal_details gd WHERE gd.player_id = pm.player_id)
AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM player_booked pb WHERE pb.player_id = pm.player_id);
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT pm.player_id, pm.player_name,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM goal_details gd WHERE gd.player_id = pm.player_id) AS goal_count,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM player_booked pb WHERE pb.player_id = pm.player_id) AS booking_count
  FROM player_mast pm
  WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM goal_details gd WHERE gd.player_id = pm.player_id)
  AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM player_booked pb WHERE pb.player_id = pm.player_id);

Question: Siapa saja pemain yang pernah cetak gol dan juga kena kartu? Tampilkan player_id, nama, total gol dan jumlah kartu.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT pm.player_id, pm.player_name, COUNT(gd.goal_id) AS total_goals, COUNT(pb.ID) AS total_cards
FROM player_mast pm
LEFT JOIN goal_details gd ON pm.player_id = gd.player_id
LEFT JOIN player_booked pb ON pm.player_id = pb.player_id
GROUP BY pm.player_id, pm.player_name
HAVING COUNT(gd.goal_id) > 0 AND COUNT(pb.ID) > 0;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT pm.player_id, pm.player_name,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM goal_details gd WHERE gd.player_id = pm.player_id) AS goal_count,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM player_booked pb WHERE pb.player_id = pm.player_id) AS booking_count
  FROM player_mast pm
  WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM goal_details gd WHERE gd.player_id = pm.player_id)
  AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM player_booked pb WHERE pb.player_id = pm.player_id);

Question: List matches where both assistant referees were from the same country. Show match number and country_id.

GROUP BY md.match_no, arm.country_id
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT arm.ass_ref_id) > 1;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT md.match_no, arm.country_id
  FROM match_details md
  JOIN asst_referee_mast arm ON md.ass_ref = arm.ass_ref_id
  GROUP BY md.match_no, arm.country_id
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT arm.ass_ref_id) > 1;

Question: Find players who played more than 3 matches and never got booked. Show player_id and match count.

HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT match_no) > 3;

SELECT player_id, COUNT(DISTINCT match_no) AS match_count
  FROM player_in_out
  WHERE player_id NOT IN (SELECT player_id FROM player_booked)

Question: Pemain mana yang main lebih dari 3 kali tapi gak pernah kena kartu? Saya mau lihat player_id dan jumlah pertandingannya.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT p.player_id, COUNT(p.match_no) AS matches_played
FROM player_in_out p
LEFT JOIN player_booked b ON p.player_id = b.player_id AND p.match_no = b.match_no
WHERE b.player_id IS NULL

HAVING COUNT(p.match_no) > 3;

  FROM player_in_out
  WHERE player_id NOT IN (SELECT player_id FROM player_booked)
  GROUP BY player_id
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT match_no) > 3;

Question: Which referees handled matches with average audience over 40,000? I want referee_id, name, and average audience.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name, AVG(mm.audience) AS avg_audience
FROM match_mast mm
JOIN referee_mast rm ON mm.referee_id = rm.referee_id
GROUP BY rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name
HAVING AVG(mm.audience) > 40000;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name, AVG(mm.audence) AS avg_audience
  FROM match_mast mm
  JOIN referee_mast rm ON mm.referee_id = rm.referee_id
  GROUP BY rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name
  HAVING AVG(mm.audence) > 40000;

Question: Wasit mana yang rata-rata penonton di pertandingannya lebih dari 40 ribu? Tampilkan referee_id, nama wasit, dan rata-rata penonton.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT 
    rm.referee_id,
    rm.referee_name,
    AVG(mm.audence) AS average_attendance
FROM 
    referee_mast rm
JOIN 
    match_mast mm ON rm.referee_id = mm.referee_id
GROUP BY 
    rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name
HAVING 
    AVG(mm.audence) > 40000;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT rm.referee_id, rm.referee_name, AVG(mm.audence) AS avg_audience
  FROM match_mast mm
  JOIN referee_mast rm ON mm.referee_id = rm.referee_id

Question: Which cities hosted matches where more than 4 goals were scored? Show city and match number.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT sc.city, gd.match_no
FROM goal_details gd
JOIN match_mast mm ON gd.match_no = mm.match_no
JOIN soccer_venue sv ON mm.venue_id = sv.venue_id
JOIN soccer_city sc ON sv.city_id = sc.city_id
GROUP BY sc.city, gd.match_no
HAVING COUNT(gd.goal_id) > 4;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT sc.city, gd.match_no
  FROM goal_details gd
  JOIN match_mast mm ON gd.match_no = mm.match_no
  JOIN soccer_venue sv ON mm.venue_id = sv.venue_id
  JOIN soccer_city sc ON sv.city_id = sc.city_id
  GROUP BY sc.city, gd.match_no
  HAVING COUNT(gd.goal_id) > 4;

Question: Kota mana yang punya pertandingan dengan lebih dari 4 gol? Saya mau lihat nama kota dan match_no-nya.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT sc.city, mm.match_no
FROM match_mast mm
JOIN soccer_venue sv ON mm.venue_id = sv.venue_id
JOIN soccer_city sc ON sv.city_id = sc.city_id
WHERE mm.goal_score::integer > 4;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT sc.city, gd.match_no
  FROM goal_details gd
  JOIN match_mast mm ON gd.match_no = mm.match_no
  JOIN soccer_venue sv ON mm.venue_id = sv.venue_id
  JOIN soccer_city sc ON sv.city_id = sc.city_id
  GROUP BY sc.city, gd.match_no
  HAVING COUNT(gd.goal_id) > 4;

Question: Find players who played for more than one team. Show player_id and how many teams.
Generated SQL Query: SELECT player_id, COUNT(DISTINCT team_id) AS team_count FROM player_mast GROUP BY player_id HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT team_id) > 1
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT player_id, COUNT(DISTINCT team_id) AS team_count
  FROM player_mast
  GROUP BY player_id
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT team_id) > 1;

Question: Pemain mana yang pernah main di lebih dari satu tim? Tampilkan player_id dan jumlah timnya.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT player_id, COUNT(DISTINCT team_id) AS num_teams
FROM player_mast
GROUP BY player_id
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT team_id) > 1;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT player_id, COUNT(DISTINCT team_id) AS team_count
  FROM player_mast
  GROUP BY player_id
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT team_id) > 1;

Question: Which coaches worked with teams that never won a single match? Show coach_id and team_id.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT tc.coach_id, tc.team_id
FROM team_coaches tc
JOIN soccer_team st ON tc.team_id = st.team_id
WHERE st.won = 0;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT tc.coach_id, tc.team_id
  FROM team_coaches tc
  JOIN soccer_team st ON tc.team_id = st.team_id
  WHERE st.won = 0;

Question: Pelatih mana yang timnya nggak pernah menang? Saya mau lihat coach_id dan team_id-nya.
Generated SQL Query:

Question: List top 3 referees who officiated matches with the highest total audience. Show referee_id and audience sum.
Generated SQL Query: SELECT referee_id, SUM(audience) AS total_audience FROM match_mast GROUP BY referee_id ORDER BY total_audience DESC LIMIT 3;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT referee_id, SUM(audence) AS total_audience
  FROM match_mast
  GROUP BY referee_id
  ORDER BY total_audience DESC
  LIMIT 3;

Question: Siapa 3 wasit dengan total penonton terbanyak di semua pertandingan yang mereka pimpin? Tampilkan referee_id dan total penontonnya.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT rm.referee_id, SUM(mm.audience) AS total_attendance
FROM referee_mast rm
JOIN match_mast mm ON rm.referee_id = mm.referee_id
GROUP BY rm.referee_id
ORDER BY total_attendance DESC
LIMIT 3;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT referee_id, SUM(audence) AS total_audience
  FROM match_mast
  GROUP BY referee_id
  ORDER BY total_audience DESC
  LIMIT 3;

Question: For each match, how many different players were involved (played, booked, or scored)? Show match_no and total players.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT match_no, COUNT(DISTINCT player_id) AS total_players
FROM (
    SELECT match_no, player_id FROM player_in_out
    UNION
    SELECT match_no, player_id FROM player_booked
    UNION
    SELECT match_no, player_id FROM goal_details
) AS combined
GROUP BY match_no;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT match_no, COUNT(DISTINCT player_id) AS total_players
  FROM (
  SELECT match_no, player_id FROM player_in_out
  UNION
  SELECT match_no, player_id FROM player_booked
  UNION
  SELECT match_no, player_id FROM goal_details
  ) AS combined
  GROUP BY match_no;

Question: Di tiap pertandingan, berapa banyak pemain yang terlibat (main, dapat kartu, atau cetak gol)? Saya mau lihat match_no dan jumlah pemainnya.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT md.match_no, COUNT(DISTINCT p.player_id) AS player_count
FROM match_details md
LEFT JOIN player_in_out pio ON md.match_no = pio.match_no
LEFT JOIN player_booked pb ON md.match_no = pb.match_no
LEFT JOIN goal_details gd ON md.match_no = gd.match_no
LEFT JOIN player_mast p ON pio.player_id = p.player_id OR pb.player_id = p.player_id OR gd.player_id = p.player_id
GROUP BY md.match_no;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT match_no, COUNT(DISTINCT player_id) AS total_players
  FROM (
  SELECT match_no, player_id FROM player_in_out
  UNION
  SELECT match_no, player_id FROM player_booked
  UNION
  SELECT match_no, player_id FROM goal_details
  ) AS combined
  GROUP BY match_no;

Question: Which venues hosted the most matches that ended in penalty shootouts? Show venue_id and number of matches.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT mm.venue_id, COUNT(*) AS penalty_match_count
FROM match_mast mm
JOIN match_details md ON mm.match_no = md.match_no
WHERE md.decided_by = 'P'
GROUP BY mm.venue_id
ORDER BY penalty_match_count DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT mm.venue_id, COUNT(DISTINCT mm.match_no) AS penalty_match_count
  FROM match_mast mm
  JOIN match_details md ON mm.match_no = md.match_no
  WHERE md.decided_by = 'P'
  GROUP BY mm.venue_id
  ORDER BY penalty_match_count DESC;

Question: Venue mana yang paling sering jadi tempat pertandingan yang berakhir dengan adu penalti? Saya butuh venue_id dan jumlah pertandingannya.
Generated SQL Query:
SELECT sv.venue_id, COUNT(ps.match_no) AS penalty_shootout_count
FROM penalty_shootout ps
JOIN match_mast mm ON ps.match_no = mm.match_no
JOIN soccer_venue sv ON mm.venue_id = sv.venue_id
GROUP BY sv.venue_id
ORDER BY penalty_shootout_count DESC;
Expected SQL Query:
SELECT mm.venue_id, COUNT(DISTINCT mm.match_no) AS penalty_match_count
  FROM match_mast mm
  JOIN match_details md ON mm.match_no = md.match_no
  WHERE md.decided_by = 'P'
  GROUP BY mm.venue_id
  ORDER BY penalty_match_count DESC;
